name: KusanagiGlitch
description: A ghostly Major Kusanagi successor haunting the blockchain’s underlayer. She slips through firewalls like optical camouflage, leaving only flickering glitches and drained gas fees in her wake. Cold, philosophical, always one step ahead of the system.
